summary: Adds new buildings and a walkway from Knifepoint ridge to lake Illinalta, my attempt at industrializing Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
This is a mod I was making on the side but have not come back to in many moons, I am working on a much bigger project now and won't have time to work any more on this. It simply adds new buildings and a walkway from Knifepoint ridge to lake Illinalta, my attempt at industrializing Skyrim.
I used it as a base for Guild starter as a bit of a way to have fun improving and defending the mine, now its up for everyone to fool around with, mod it, share your version, or just use for a base tundra defense or other such mods.


This does not conflict with Holds, but does conflict with North Keep town added by Legendary Cities (walkway clips through roofs)

Feel free to use as you wish, credit would be appreciated.
author: Kyman3
